metadata.title: Bell 47
aws::graph::propositions: G-AZYB is a Bell 47H helicopter on static display at the Helicopter Museum in Weston-super-Mare, Somerset, United Kingdom.
G-AZYB is painted in former SABENA markings as OO-SHW.
G-AZYB supported a scientific expedition in Antarctica.

LV-AEF is a Bell 47B-3 helicopter on static display at the Niagara Aerospace Museum in Niagara Falls, New York, United States.

text:
United Kingdom
G-AZYB (painted in former SABENA markings as OO-SHW)  Bell 47H on static display at the Helicopter Museum in Weston-super-Mare, Somerset. It supported a scientific expedition in Antarctica.
